import { Box, Container,  Grid2, Typography} from "@mui/material"
import React from "react"
import Divider, { dividerClasses } from '@mui/material/Divider';

import Input from "../../component/Input"
import SendIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Send"
import Qrimagefooter from "../../image/Frame 719.png"

import LinkedInIcon from "@mui/icons-material/LinkedIn"
import {styled} from '@mui/system'

const FooterBox = styled(Box)`
  background-color: black;
  padding: 30px 0px 30px 0px;
  position: relative;
  top: 333px;
`

const FooterInput = styled(Box)`
  border: 1px solid white;
  width: 210px;
  height: 46px;
  margin-top: 16px;
`
// const Footimg = styled(Image)`
//   width: 204px;
//   height: 85px;
// `

const ConatinerFooter = styled(Container)`
  margin-top: 40px;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
`

const StyledDivider=styled(Divider)(({theme})=>({
    border:`1px solid ${theme.palette.primary.main}`
}))
const Footimg=styled("img")(()=>({
    
    width:" 204px",
   height: "85px"
}))

export default function Footer() {

            </Grid2>
            <Grid2 size={2}>

        <Box textAlign={"center"}>
        <Typography variant="subtitle2" sx={{color:"gray",mt:2}}>
          ©  CopyWrite Rimel 2025.All

    </Typography>
